(text "LAYOUT-CRITICAL NOTES:" (at 20.32 449.58 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3d985a38-151c-5f18-b07e-f10b61844237))
(text "Place L901/C911/C912/C913/R907 exactly around U901 per Raspberry Pi RP2350 guidance; keep LX copper tiny." (at 20.32 457.2 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid de342645-750c-5503-b6cd-a5a50428b642))
(text "Place R900/R901 at U901 USB pins and U906 in the short Mu path; route both pairs as 90-ohm differential over uninterrupted ground." (at 20.32 464.82 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c0b8690e-b1fb-5d51-87bc-e696d8ab9226))
(text "Keep Y900/R906/C918/C919 tight to XIN/XOUT. Keep QSPI traces short; place C902/C903 at U902." (at 20.32 472.44 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 67234476-dba0-5395-9156-cf87c4aa78cf))
(text "No Pico module, Micro-USB receptacle, or internal USB cable is used. The integrated RP2350 is the USB device." (at 20.32 480.06 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid aea5ddf1-e059-5257-a7fc-ea864b55b15a))
(text "J901 is keyed/latching JST PUD 2.00mm and NOT Pi-HAT compatible. U910-U913 isolate and tolerate 5V at the connector; 5.5V-standoff U914-U921 provide connector-side ESD." (at 20.32 487.68 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid db998c1a-9b1a-5873-8bec-4c1c69a4637a))
(text "R932-R961 are 330R fault-limit resistors. Digital outputs are 3.3V only; use external I2C pull-ups >=4.7k and initially keep SPI/SWD <=10MHz." (at 20.32 495.3 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ad9c7d37-c620-5bc8-9b09-61b04e34ecaa))
(text "The ADC reference remains internal. J901 ADC precision range is 0-3.0V; 5.5V tolerance is for accidental input only and must be validated, not treated as an ADC range." (at 20.32 502.92 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 93df4d2f-5c04-5fa6-9acb-eaafc2e67e85))
(text "U922/Q903 hold all 30 signals disconnected until MAKER_3V3_CORE is valid. Header power rails separately default OFF and are current-limited." (at 20.32 510.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ddae3ce7-18c8-5a47-9d05-fddc1e727df8))
(text "U906 defaults disconnected and connects only after physical INTERNAL_USB_VBUS is valid. The maker cannot wake S3; firmware reinitializes USB when MAKER_HOST_ACTIVE_N falls." (at 20.32 518.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid b3539a8c-e989-582c-a797-c0d1500a71da))
